sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Endpoint
    participant Handler
    participant HybridSearch as Hybrid Search Service
    participant Qdrant as Qdrant (Vector DB)
    participant Postgres as PostgreSQL (FTS)
    participant Reranker as Cross-Encoder Reranker
    participant LLM as Multi-Model LLM
    participant Redis

    Client->>Endpoint: POST /api/v1/knowledge-base/ask
    Note right of Client: {gameId, question, language}

    Endpoint->>Handler: Handle(AskQuestionQuery)

    Handler->>Redis: Check cache?
    Redis-->>Handler: Cache miss

    Note over Handler,Reranker: Stage 1: Hybrid Retrieval (ADR-001)

    par Parallel Retrieval
        Handler->>Qdrant: Vector search (semantic)
        Qdrant-->>Handler: Top-20 chunks (vector scores)
    and
        Handler->>Postgres: Keyword search (FTS)
        Postgres-->>Handler: Top-20 chunks (BM25 scores)
    end

    Handler->>HybridSearch: RRF Fusion (70% vector + 30% keyword)
    HybridSearch-->>Handler: Merged top-10 chunks

    Note over Handler,Reranker: Stage 2: Cross-Encoder Reranking

    Handler->>Reranker: Rerank top-10
    Reranker-->>Handler: Top-3 chunks (relevance scores)

    Note over Handler,LLM: Stage 3: Multi-Model Generation (ADR-007)

    par Parallel LLM Calls
        Handler->>LLM: GPT-4 generate answer
        LLM-->>Handler: Answer A (confidence: 0.87)
    and
        Handler->>LLM: Claude generate answer
        LLM-->>Handler: Answer B (confidence: 0.91)
    and
        Handler->>LLM: DeepSeek generate answer
        LLM-->>Handler: Answer C (confidence: 0.85)
    end

    Handler->>Handler: Consensus voting (select highest confidence)
    Handler->>Handler: Final confidence = (0.87 + searchConf) / 2

    alt Final Confidence ≥ 0.70
        Handler->>Redis: Cache result (10 min)
        Handler-->>Client: 200 OK {answer, sources, confidence: 0.88}
    else Low Quality (< 0.70)
        Handler-->>Client: 200 OK {answer, isLowQuality: true, confidence: 0.62}
    end
